      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;terraform-best-practices-for-production-infrastructure&#34;&gt;Terraform Best Practices for Production Infrastructure&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Infrastructure as Code (IaC) with Terraform has revolutionized how we manage cloud resources. Here are the essential practices I&amp;rsquo;ve learned from managing production infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;state-management&#34;&gt;State Management&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;remote-state-storage&#34;&gt;Remote State Storage&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Always use remote state storage for production environments:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;table style=&#34;border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 2&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 3&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 4&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 5&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 6&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 7&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 8&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt; 9&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#737679&#34;&gt;10&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#e6edf3;background-color:#0d1117;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-hcl&#34; data-lang=&#34;hcl&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff7b72&#34;&gt;terraform&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff7b72&#34;&gt;backend&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a5d6ff&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;s3&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    bucket &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff7b72;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a5d6ff&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;my-terraform-state&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    key    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff7b72;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a5d6ff&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;production/terraform.tfstate&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    regio